An 11-year-old girl is  in an East London hospital after she was mauled by a neighbour’s pit bull. Rekeisha-Lee Barnes was playing with  friends on Thursday afternoon in her Breidbach home  8km outside Qonce (King William’s Town), when the  dog  entered the fenced yard. It was not clear how the dog managed to gain entry to the yard. For more on this article, please visit DispatchLIVE.